text: František Rydval (born 21 February 1946) is a Czech ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1946 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Czechoslovakia Category:Ski jumpers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Liberec
